HOW TO INSTALL X-RAI

Pre-requisite
=============

In order to install x-rai, you need:
- a web server (apache)
- PHP with PEAR, modules: postgresql, xslt
- a postgresql server
- perl, bash

Installing
==========

Decompress the archive. The web directory is the only one that have to be published by
the web server, through a link for example with UNIX.

Change the name of "settings-template.inc" to "settings.inc" in web/include, and edit that
file with the corresponding values.